@startuml
title Configuration (Assembly Pattern)

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Reify (make explicit) the assembly of objects forming a composite/complex structure (often via configuration/metadata/DI).

**Use when**: You want to externalize wiring of object graphs (DI containers, config files).

**Key participants**: Configuration, Configurator, Component, Composite.
endlegend

interface Component {
  +operation()
}

class Leaf
class Composite {
  +add(c: Component)
  +operation()
}

class Configuration <<data>> {
  +definitions
}

class Configurator {
  +build(config: Configuration) : Component
}

Component <|.. Leaf
Component <|.. Composite
Composite *-- Component : children
Configurator ..> Configuration : reads
Configurator ..> Composite : assembles
@enduml